text: This is a list of rivers, which are at least partially in Liechtenstein. * Rhine/Rhein, flows into the North Sea. It forms most the country's border with Switzerland. * Samina River/Saminabach, flows into the Ill. It starts in Liechtenstein and continues into Austria. * Liechtenstein Liechtenstein Category:Liechtenstein-related lists
title: List of rivers of Liechtenstein
